page.title: 32Clubs
page.content:
Come along to Havant and do something artistic. All seasons are free!! And suitable for girls and boys of all abilities. There are lots of free art clubs. This club is always on Tuesdays in aug. if you want to do tennis you need to be between the age 8 and 15. if you do want to do this club it is on every day of the week except Saturday and Sunday, this club takes place at warblington in august. Cheerleading is suitable for girls and boys! It your chance to learn new and exciting cheerleading routines.


Tess and Luke
